  "texts": [
    "CDD-CESMCDD-CESM is a newly introduced publicly available dataset that provides images in two types FDDM and CESM.",
    "It is the first publicly available dataset that contains CESM images.",
    "The dataset includes 2006 images divided into 1003 low-energy images (FDDM) and 1003 subtracted images representing the (CESM).",
    "The dataset has MLO and CC view images; the images were acquired using two different scanners that are G.E.",
    "Healthcare Senographe DS and Hologic Selenia Dimensions Mammography Systems."
  ],
